I deleted unclear and wrong information - there is much debate about the origins of Caffa, but Feodisia was a ruin until the Genoese were granted it by the Golden Horde, probably sometime in the 1260s. The Venetian attack on Caffa in 1296 was unsuccessful as far as I'm aware, and the Venetians never ruled here.
